  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal, no COU)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package conforms to ProfileMinimal and intentionally omits hasContextOfUse, leaving the intended-use scope undefined. Full 13-factor assessment included; Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed. Decision: Accepted.",
